Scribble v4.1.0

What's new,
- Now you can modify access permission for specific notes (Read Only)

Scribble v4.0

What's new,
- Database migrated to SQLite for improved reliability and performance.
- Full-text search enabled across note title and content.
- Search matches are highlighted within notes.
- Notes can be sorted by date created and date modified.
- Notes can be deleted, archived, and bookmarked.
- Deleted, archived, and bookmarked notes are accessible from the navigation drawer.

